    {
     "type": "char",
     "marker": "add",
     "content": [
      "âdestroy"
     ]
    },
    " those who are more ",
    {
     "type": "char",
     "marker": "add",
     "content": [
      "âgodly"
     ]
    },
    " than them?â (1:13). God answered that he would step in and help in due course: ââŠgodly people live by their faith.â (2:4)\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "type": "para",
   "marker": "ip",
   "content": [
